    <description>Business use: Used to trigger all the actions once an advice record has been cancelled. Including closing all tasks, closing related fulfilment and recommendations. If the reason for cancelling advice is that the customer is withdrawing from onboarding, then this will kick off the cancel onboarding process. 
Tech use: If client wants to leave us then the creation of the case will trigger the Case | cancel onboarding flow to initiate the cancel onboarding process</description>
